# next-intl TimeZone Configuration Fix
**Date:** 2025-10-10
**Branch:** odavl/site-hotfix-20251010
**Issue:** ENVIRONMENT_FALLBACK warning - no timeZone configured

## Problem Analysis
- next-intl components (useTranslations, useLocale) require consistent timeZone
- Missing timeZone causes server/client environment differences
- Results in ENVIRONMENT_FALLBACK warnings in console

## Solution Applied
1. Added timeZone: 'UTC' to src/i18n/request.ts config
2. Added timeZone="UTC" to SafeIntlProvider component
3. Ensures consistent timezone across server and client

## Files Modified
- src/i18n/request.ts: Add timeZone configuration
- src/components/SafeIntlProvider.tsx: Add timeZone prop

## Expected Result
✅ No more ENVIRONMENT_FALLBACK warnings
✅ Consistent server/client rendering
✅ Stable timezone behavior across locales